<document>
  <header>
    <title>USPS Intelligent Mail (4-State Customer Barcode)</title>
  </header>
  <body>
    <section id="example">
      <title>Example</title>
      <figure src="../images/example-usps4cb.png" alt="Example USPS Intelligent Mail Customer Barcode symbol"/>
    </section>
    <section id="structure">
      <title>Structure</title>
      <p>The configuration for the default implementation is:</p>
      <source>&#60;barcode&#62;
    &#60;<strong>usps4cb</strong>&#62;
        &#60;module-width&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:0.020in}&#60;/module-width&#62;
        &#60;track-height&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:0.050in}&#60;/track-height&#62;
        &#60;ascender-height&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:0.050in}&#60;/ascender-height&#62;
        &#60;interchar-gap-width&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:0.025in}&#60;/interchar-gap-width&#62;
        &#60;quiet-zone enabled="{<link href="barcode-xml.html#boolean">boolean</link>:true}"&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:0.125in}&#60;/quiet-zone&#62;
        &#60;vertical-quiet-zone&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:0.028in}&#60;/vertical-quiet-zone&#62;
        &#60;human-readable&#62;
            &#60;placement&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#human-readable-placement">human-readable-placement</link>:none}&#60;/placement&#62;
            &#60;font-name&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#font-name">font-name</link>:Helvetica}&#60;/font-name&#62;
            &#60;font-size&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:8pt}&#60;/font-size&#62;
        &#60;/human-readable&#62;
    &#60;/<strong>usps4cb</strong>&#62;
&#60;/barcode&#62;</source>
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>Notes</title>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Please refer to the symbol specification for information about the valid ranges
          of the above configuration values.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>Message format</title>
      <ul>
        <li>Valid characters are 0-9</li>
        <li>All other character all automatically removed for processing.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>Links</title>
      <ul>
        <li>Specification: <link href="http://ribbs.usps.gov/OneCodeSolution/">http://ribbs.usps.gov/OneCodeSolution/</link></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </body>
</document>

